1)  start an empty node project:
    npm init -y

2)  npm install colyseus @colyseus/schema express
    npm install @colyseus/tools --save-dev
    npm install typescript ts-node @types/node @types/express --save-dev

3)  Initialise typescript
    npx tsc --init

4)  Setup project structure -> Add src folder

5)  npm install dotenv
    npm install playfab-sdk 
    npm install axios 